# id: 7
# title: The Captain's Log
# chinese_title: 船长日记
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

A personal terminal still holds the final logs of a long-dead captain. Her words paint a picture of desperate last days — rationing supplies, sealing off sections, watching the stars for rescue that never came. Among the entries, she left coordinates to her personal cache.

* [Follow the coordinates to her cache]
  ~ gain_gold(35)
  "宝" (bǎo) — treasure, precious
* [Read the full log for historical insights]
  ~ gain_radical("言")
  "言" (yán) — speech, words, to say
* [Copy the log for the archives]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "记" (jì) — to record, to remember
